Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:20.74,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年少女结成圆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:24.67,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出的手划过又落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:29.21,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法交错的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:31.39,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋转木马在空中旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:35.52,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的帷幕徐徐落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:38.04,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密揭晓的神圣之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:44.13,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜开窗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:49.29,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤秘密的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.90,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀起深红的窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:59.15,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐去微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.64,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年啊 回归自我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.94,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上特快列车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.51,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去梦幻之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:14.10,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:16.51,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被指指点点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:20.26,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以立刻逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:29.16,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一切中意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.53,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年少女结成圆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:36.30,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出的手划过又落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.68,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮回的命运
