Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:08.66,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你那深邃眼眸中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:16.80,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然有着刻骨铭心的记忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:25.43,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏着爱 寻找着爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.16,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自忍受孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:38.55,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说无欲无求 那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:44.03,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hide and  seek 希望就在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:54.44,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hide and  seek 尽情绽放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:03.26,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hide and  seek 相互憎恨着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:07.75,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hide and  seek 欲哭无泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:11.89,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我与你共眠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
